section bg-slate-50 py-24 sm:py-32 > . mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8
  . mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0
    h2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl "From the Fieldnotes blog"
    p mt-2 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600
      | Engineering deep dives, launch stories, and hard-won lessons from building agricultural sensing at scale.
  . mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3
    article group flex flex-col items-start
      a(href=/blog/soil-probe-v3) relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl
        img(src=/img/blog/soil-probe-field.jpg alt="") aspect-[16/9] w-full bg-slate-200 object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-105
        . absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-900/10
      . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs
        time(datetime=2026-06-18) text-slate-500 "Jun 18, 2026"
        a(href=/blog/category/hardware) rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 "Hardware"
      h3 mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-700 > a(href=/blog/soil-probe-v3) "Designing a soil probe that survives five winters underground"
      p mt-3 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600
        | Frost heave destroyed 30% of our v2 probes in the first season. Here's how a redesigned housing, a new potting compound, and one counterintuitive antenna decision got failures under 1%.
      . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-3
        img(src=/img/team/anna.jpg alt="") h-9 w-9 rounded-full bg-slate-200 object-cover
        . text-sm leading-5
          p font-semibold text-slate-900 "Anna Delgado"
          p text-slate-600 "Head of Hardware"
    article group flex flex-col items-start
      a(href=/blog/lora-mesh-lessons) relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl
        img(src=/img/blog/lora-gateway.jpg alt="") aspect-[16/9] w-full bg-slate-200 object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-105
        . absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-900/10
      . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs
        time(datetime=2026-05-30) text-slate-500 "May 30, 2026"
        a(href=/blog/category/engineering) rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 "Engineering"
      h3 mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-700 > a(href=/blog/lora-mesh-lessons) "What 40,000 LoRa nodes taught us about mesh networking"
      p mt-3 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600
        | Textbook mesh routing collapses when half your nodes sleep 99% of the time. We walk through the scheduling protocol that cut packet loss from 12% to 0.4% across our largest deployment.
      . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-3
        img(src=/img/team/tomas.jpg alt="") h-9 w-9 rounded-full bg-slate-200 object-cover
        . text-sm leading-5
          p font-semibold text-slate-900 "Tomas Novak"
          p text-slate-600 "Staff Firmware Engineer"
    article group flex flex-col items-start
      a(href=/blog/irrigation-savings-study) relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl
        img(src=/img/blog/pivot-irrigation.jpg alt="") aspect-[16/9] w-full bg-slate-200 object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-105
        . absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-900/10
      . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs
        time(datetime=2026-05-12) text-slate-500 "May 12, 2026"
        a(href=/blog/category/research) rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 "Research"
      h3 mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-700 > a(href=/blog/irrigation-savings-study) "Two seasons of data: sensor-driven irrigation cut water use 31%"
      p mt-3 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600
        | Results from our study with 14 Nebraska corn growers, including the full methodology, the fields where it didn't work, and what that means for scheduling models.
      . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-3
        img(src=/img/team/grace.jpg alt="") h-9 w-9 rounded-full bg-slate-200 object-cover
        . text-sm leading-5
          p font-semibold text-slate-900 "Grace Okafor"
          p text-slate-600 "Agronomy Research Lead"
